overview:
eMaletas is an online retailer of luggage, travel goods and travel accessories.

We sell all types of products related to travel: From suitcases to bags, rucksacks, holdalls, wallets, briefcases, laptop cases and travel accesories. We offer a wide range of the most famous brands at the best prices: Samsonite, Delsey, Roncato, Tumi, The North Face, Hello Kitty, Piquadro and more.

All of our products are new, original and purchased directly from the manufacturers of these majors brands. Thanks to this, our customers are guaranteed to receive high quality products.

Our headquarters are located in Barcelona (Spain), but we can offer our products and services worldwide.
